title: Episode 4 w/ Gunplay and Capone
itunes:title: Episode 4 w/ Gunplay and Capone
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN drink it up with Maybach Music / Def Jam recording artist Gunplay and legendary Queens Bridge rapper Capone of Capone-n-Noreaga. The guys drink it up and discuss everything from Prison, to the Meek and Drake beef, issues with Mobb Deep and more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
